### Test Query Suggestions Endpoint Fix

@baseUrl = https://localhost:7189
@connectionId = c1034bfe-ede7-4291-8ba2-0feef5c75fd5
@token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Test 1: Get Query Suggestions for Employees table
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/db-explorer/{{connectionId}}/tables/Employees/suggestions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Expected Response:
# {
#   "suggestions": [
#     {
#       "title": "Find all employees",
#       "query": "SELECT * FROM Employees",
#       "category": "basic",
#       "complexity": "simple"
#     },
#     ...
#   ]
# }

### Test 2: Get Query Suggestions for Categories table
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/db-explorer/{{connectionId}}/tables/Categories/suggestions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Test 3: Get Query Suggestions for Products table
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/db-explorer/{{connectionId}}/tables/Products/suggestions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Test 4: Invalid table name (should return 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/db-explorer/{{connectionId}}/tables/InvalidTable/suggestions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Expected: 404 Not Found with error message

### Test 5: No cached schema (should return 400)
# First clear cache, then try to get suggestions
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/db-explorer/{{connectionId}}/cache
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/db-explorer/{{connectionId}}/tables/Employees/suggestions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Expected: 400 Bad Request with "Schema not cached" message

### Test 6: Re-analyze and try again
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/db-explorer/{{connectionId}}/analyze?forceRefresh=true
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/db-explorer/{{connectionId}}/tables/Employees/suggestions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Expected: 200 OK with suggestions array
